{"tid":9722,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"樣定性格重要啲？","createTime":"2016-11-28T16:29:58.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-07T07:50:28.000Z","uid":14932,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"699b72c872e853a11ed5bf4eadcef18267fa4968","tid":9722,"uid":14932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:29:58.000Z","msg":"其實外表係咪真係咁重要<br />\n重要嘅定係人地點睇？<br />\n如果你真係鐘意一個人 其他嘢已經唔重要啦係咪<br />\n識咗一個人唔知佢咩樣但同佢幾岩傾 又係我想要個類型<br />\n但擔心自己望到佢個樣就會即刻扣哂分 我認我係外貌協會 但又會諗就算俾我遇到個令仔但唔夾 前者會唔會好啲<br />\n好矛盾 有冇人都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7db6272c88cdb15243214e6c897b39e793263e6","tid":9722,"uid":2154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:31:12.000Z","msg":"Feel 重要啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aaed7b10b24d4ad71424c32c4273e0403be7bfb","tid":9722,"uid":36412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:32:46.000Z","msg":"十靚歲既會睇樣<br />\n當出左黎社會就想睇重性格<br />\n我中學時都覺得百行以樣行先<br />\n但升左去ive 大撚把複製港女就覺得性格重要得多"},{"pid":"e5b28bb9cf54d9154b047f796906116fe2758552","tid":9722,"uid":15339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:33:15.000Z","msg":"對你黎講就重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0adbf110083450eb69345ba4ff0092896effb6d2","tid":9722,"uid":28590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:34:32.000Z","msg":"樣係一開始個種吸引力<br />\n吸引到你認識佢<br />\n所以都要順眼 合眼緣<br />\n<br />\n性格係長遠<br />\n睇兩個人合唔合得黎囉"},{"pid":"120880bbd33d0a9d6b580bbe0df75818035d6158","tid":9722,"uid":25677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:34:37.000Z","msg":"其實靚唔靚仔無所謂，最緊要你覺得順眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果你第一眼見佢覺得柒既，咁你遲早會嫌棄佢<br />\n我個人就係樣當然都睇，不過就算佢幾靚 性格唔得一定唔會中意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68d775149bcb46d9cd1e40169021dabdde1fefd6","tid":9722,"uid":2065,"like":